the hard-boiled canary is a 1941 american musical comedy film directed by andrew l. stone and written by robert lively and andrew l. stone .   it was later reissued as there 's magic in music .   the film stars allan jones , susanna foster , margaret lindsay , lynne overman , grace bradley , william collier , sr. and heimo haitto .   it was released on june 8 , 1941 , by paramount pictures .